            <div class="c-modal-body">
                <h3 class="u-m-1">Why Adobe Fundamentals?</h3>
                <p>Every business, whether small or large, should start with a basic set of unchangeable principles; something to fall back on when challenges arise. Yet rapid expansion can make entrepreneurs feel like the spirit and values of their company are cast aside. Adobe would like to inspire businesses from all industries to find their own fundamentals, by sharing remarkable stories featuring companies determined to stick to the basics, at any cost.</p>
                <p>That's why we’ve created Fundamentals, an ongoing series looking at different companies worldwide and the basic principles they were built on.</p>
                <p><a href="https://www.adobe.com/creativecloud/business/teams/business-features.html?sdid=B8NR3R9F&mv=display" data-event-category="Channel" data-event-action= "adobe-fundamentals" data-event-label="CTA - Learn how to design and deliver amazing customer experiences with Creative Cloud for teams" target="_blank">Learn how to design and deliver amazing customer experiences with Creative Cloud for teams.</a></p>
